Explicit Version. We Global is the third album by Miami based producer DJ 
Khaled. Guest appearances include Rick Ross, Ace Hood, Plies, Young Jeezy, 
T.I., Lil Wayne, Akon, Trick Daddy, Lil Boosie, Nas, Cool & Dre, Kanye West, 
Fabolous, Fat Joe, Chris Brown, Sean Paul, Brisco, Busta Rhymes, Flo Rida, 
and many more. Khaled Khaled born in New Orleans, Louisiana, is better 
known by his stage name DJ Khaled is a Palestinian-American DJ, record 
producer, and radio personality for the South Florida radio station WEDR 99 
Jamz. He was also member of the Hip Hop group Terror Squad.
